You wake up on what appears to be the top floor of a castle in a turret, with nothing in it but an ornate carpet.
Rain lashes against the shuttered windows and the only lighting is a high chandelier with very dim, fluttering candles.
You can't remember anything, not how you got there or even what your name is.  Your attention is captured by a purple
liquid that dots the floor.  You follow it to its source...